text: Private property is a legal designation for the ownership of property by non- governmental legal entities. Private property may also refer to: * Private Property (1960 film), an American film starring Kate Manx, Warren Oates and Corey Allen. * Private Property (2006 film), a French-language Belgian film directed by Joachim Lafosse. ==See also== * Property rights (economics) * Anti-capitalism
title: Private property (disambiguation)
